llraiser_Poster.jpg&h=4f1a1b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.賴瑞與第二任妻子茱莉亞(Julia)搬入新家，然而賴瑞卻不知道茱莉亞早與自己的兄弟法蘭克有染，茱莉亞得知情人法蘭克被一個神秘的魔盒殺死，需要人血獻祭才能復活，便開始勾引獵殺無辜的男人，另一方面，賴瑞的女兒克莉絲汀(Kirsty)撿到了魔盒，不小心釋放出「針頭」等地獄修道士們......<br />\n<br />\n2.克莉絲汀進了精神病院，遇到了沉迷於邪術研究的查納德醫生，他不但以人血將邪惡的茱莉亞復活，還利用自閉症女孩蒂芬妮解開魔盒，開啟地獄之門，闖入地獄世界的克莉絲汀與蒂芬妮等人能全身而退嗎.....?<br />\n<br />\n3.女記者喬伊目賭一樁鐵鍊殺人慘案，決心要查出真相，而調查途中又牽扯出了針頭鬼欲復活並且將人間化為地獄的陰謀，眼看針頭大開殺戒，喬伊能阻止他嗎?而不斷出現在喬伊夢中的神秘男子艾略特．史賓賽將會是打敗針頭的關鍵...?<br />\n<br />\n12 40AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=242b717d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=92120bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75bf6142afa982dfbf27e5db09a2676c0628190","tid":2015452,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf237eda9da1fad3c01ef39484a79590b18fd259","tid":2015452,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4a